  <div class="c-entry-hero__header-wrap">
    <h1 class="c-page-title">For the sake of national security, Donald Trump needs to trade in his cellphone</h1>

    
  </div>
  <h2 class="c-entry-summary p-dek">Heâs going to have to give up most of the features that make a smartphone smart.</h2>

  
    <div class="c-byline">
  
    By
    <span class="c-byline__item">
      
        
        <a href="https://www.recode.net/authors/ina-fried">Ina Fried</a> and <a href="https://www.recode.net/authors/april-glaser">April Glaser</a>
      
    </span>
    
