  <source srcset="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/jWHkdW-Q9IpDnUBAXumHHiOvqOc=/0x0:5162x3441/320x213/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NY3Dr2WJUixVOHskCYN3RvJALWE=/0x0:5162x3441/620x413/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 620w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/d1JIirrDuWZ2QrpmeelYKdTqcG0=/0x0:5162x3441/920x613/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RoBALsCcnMitwCJKOKCvlb4U-d4=/0x0:5162x3441/1220x813/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 1220w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/AEsHguwZ08l9Eq15qJyV-GLN3wI=/0x0:5162x3441/1520x1013/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/FOYj6e6-sqLYn8FZ_glvptuvyec=/0x0:5162x3441/1820x1213/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 1820w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/81sKZX4w48KkhvzV29AfJNmNMns=/0x0:5162x3441/2120x1413/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 2120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/oPJjwmj3rVQVXDdjdyFGF_JfbsI=/0x0:5162x3441/2420x1613/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 2420w" sizes="(min-width: 1221px) 846px, (min-width: 880px) calc(100vw - 334px), 100vw" type="image/webp">


<img srcset="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/DtZXQJNBrA0aEps_NiE-gyL5fh4=/0x0:5162x3441/320x213/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4o1iIbiT_6cCTJuXCEN4xbuLUck=/0x0:5162x3441/620x413/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 620w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/FNWiEih7ZPlhfIkhdZvw0LCPdBM=/0x0:5162x3441/920x613/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/2PSu8KiYbbPYax4-dxsPlQ8OO04=/0x0:5162x3441/1220x813/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 1220w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/KQOIWo5Wlxqvr__8eOAM5kLSfDk=/0x0:5162x3441/1520x1013/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/AlPhT2oqbnKbz-EigNCzy_65gHc=/0x0:5162x3441/1820x1213/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 1820w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/C0O1ue1seefPHK4k9qBAtAuhZ5M=/0x0:5162x3441/2120x1413/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 2120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/AcYAqMqsFOjlQtiXzipnxeebou0=/0x0:5162x3441/2420x1613/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg 2420w" sizes="(min-width: 1221px) 846px, (min-width: 880px) calc(100vw - 334px), 100vw" alt="" style="object-position: 50% 50%" data-upload-width="5162" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Xphp7oSIe327-hynx_2cXjYk274=/0x0:5162x3441/1200x800/filters:focal(2169x1309:2993x2133)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/52828787/trump_phones.0.0.jpg">

</source></picture>

      
    </span>
    
  </span>
  
    <span class="e-image__meta">
      
      
        <cite>Photo illustration by Recode (with photos from Getty Images, Samsung and BlackBerry)</cite>
      
    </span>
  
</figure>

    






<div class="c-entry-content ">
  <p id="PojP83">The question of what phone a president carries â and what he or she does with it â is a serious matter of national security. </p>
<p id="xDLzS1">Take a president who likes to make policy announcements on Twitter at three in the morning and the matter becomes even more urgent. </p>
<p id="9YxD9k">After all, when Donald Trump tweets, <a href="http://www.detroitnews.com/story/business/2017/01/18/stock-traders-use-algorithms-cash-trump-tweets/96736956/">the stock market shifts</a>. If someone were to read what he was preparing to tweet by breaking into his smartphone and using keylogging software, even with just a 30-second head start, it could make some people very rich and potentially cause serious damage to the national economy. </p>
<p id="edoIKZ">And, of course, thereâs the matter of the presidentâs physical safety, as well as the risk of classified information being compromised and of someone trying to hack the phone to get the presidentâs account credentials.</p>
<p id="64CTCf">As president-elect, Trump has continued to use <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/donald-trump-waits-in-his-tower--accessible-yet-isolated/2017/01/16/7697fdd8-d9a4-11e6-9f9f-5cdb4b7f8dd7_story.html?postshare=5321484660564175&amp;tid=ss_tw&amp;utm_term=.cd1340f86d84">his Android device as his primary means </a>for both keeping in touch with associates and expressing his displeasure with news outlets and âSaturday Night Live.â </p>
<p id="3vH2kp">But experts say that, as president, Trump really needs to use something a whole lot more secure.</p>
<p id="0nrtWe">Weâve asked the transition team what kind of smartphone Donald Trump intends to use when he assumes the Oval Office on Friday and have yet to get a response. </p>
<p id="fnX883">Trump wonât have to figure this out on his own. Thereâs even <a href="http://disa.mil/careers/whca">an agency specifically tasked</a> with supporting the presidentâs telecommunications needs, the White House Communications Agency. And the Secret Service, which has to protect the president, is likely to weigh in as well.</p>
<p id="WCoY4I">As to whether government agencies can force Trump to give up his current phone, itâs complicated. Trump may resist technical security measures imposed on him by the Secret Service. However, <a href="https://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/text/18/3056">by law</a>, their protection of the president is mandatory and cannot be declined. </p>
<p id="OOnrlO">(That said, the <a href="https://www.secretservice.gov/about/leadership/">president appoints</a> the director of the Secret Service, as well as the secretary of Homeland Security and other department heads, so the power dynamics are less than simple.)</p>
<p id="QniKej">Hereâs what outside security experts say Trumpâs phone should look like:</p>
<p id="dctr62"><strong>The </strong><strong>p</strong><strong>residentâs phone should not be connected to the internet</strong>, according to Matthew Green, a cryptographer and professor of computer science at Johns Hopkins<strong>. </strong>This may seem obvious, but itâs worth reiterating. Everything connected to the internet is vulnerable to attack.</p>
<p id="RWdGri">That means no tweeting. It also means Trump is probably going to have to go Android, since itâs not possible to sufficiently customize an iPhone. Instead, Trump may end up with a phone that, like Obamaâs, can really only be used to call or message a small group of trusted aides and family.</p>
<p id="SBoV78">If Trump or his aides insist on carrying commercial-grade phones, they should <strong>never be taken into high-level meetings, </strong>since there are known exploits that can power on the deviceâs microphone, Tom Lowenthal, a digital security technologist at the Committee to Protect Journalists, told <strong>Recode</strong>. </p>
<p id="ZD32IN">During the Obama administration, there were boxes outside the rooms in the Old Executive Office Building where cellphones could be stored when even the most basic national security matters might be discussed.</p>
<div class="c-float-right">  <figure class="e-image">
  <span class="e-image__inner">
    <span class="e-image__image " data-original="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg">
      
        <picture class="c-picture" data-cid="site/picture_element-1554398250_9342_9165" data-cdata='{"asset_id":7836309,"ratio":"*"}'>
  


  <source srcset="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HRlodus6ZOP7IjgSCXfE6nwgDN8=/0x0:801x1068/320x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/M-Xur_kWuGOnHIfDKWyUAZT5hZY=/0x0:801x1068/520x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wtvtVjxRgcoUTPD79m8b8IhImBA=/0x0:801x1068/720x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/KvlldTI1NPKRpfBVg2weUlz6_c0=/0x0:801x1068/920x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HMvlaJvemQHFEP39_nJ_k4RTv9c=/0x0:801x1068/1120x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 1120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/jbR-_kZYZL_mzXbPXC_h_dZxcJI=/0x0:801x1068/1320x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 1320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wmcQQSt_Dkba8c4qQXttfvjQlLI=/0x0:801x1068/1520x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Y39KRCqzX8osJ5o6jWgQfkeZuvA=/0x0:801x1068/1720x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 1720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/EFzXcCC5sEX4OEQbBwJR8_nA94k=/0x0:801x1068/1920x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 1920w" sizes="(min-width: 1221px) 846px, (min-width: 880px) calc(100vw - 334px), 100vw" type="image/webp">


<img srcset="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/1nqj3srAQmhn7LVU03YxKva7Qu4=/0x0:801x1068/320x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/xP3nd6uUZmOlBowbnzLumpN6Aew=/0x0:801x1068/520x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ttrPZCQT52Nu3IkBzkIGIe6vAFA=/0x0:801x1068/720x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/kWCRjdzdeEVouPLXsqtOsakeHsA=/0x0:801x1068/920x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/oV2-_erDSTYyUH9YxVCRooly4lk=/0x0:801x1068/1120x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 1120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/t8MU6WbTEBzN6oXGAoT-rfFLosI=/0x0:801x1068/1320x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 1320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JL8D_OVGrIxBpx5DvsBu-MlQaRA=/0x0:801x1068/1520x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9-9-C1gh4rj_9MWLGog1Cvtny8I=/0x0:801x1068/1720x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 1720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/bKZ85qx0M8_ksPNI8_NYlAYTNRg=/0x0:801x1068/1920x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7836309/phone_box.jpg 1920w" sizes="(min-width: 1221px) 846px, (min-width: 880px) calc(100vw - 334px), 100vw" alt="" style="object-position: 49% 50%" data-upload-width="801" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/97wbhKxH4nEzoy5m6n2fOzBade8=/0x0:801x1068/1200x0/filters:focal(0x0:801x1068)